# SaaS Optimizer Desktop App

🖥️ **Native device integration** for the SaaS Optimizer platform.

## Features

- 📧 **Email Scanner** - Reads Mail.app, Outlook, Thunderbird receipts
- 📱 **SMS Reader** - Accesses Messages.app or Android SMS via ADB  
- 📸 **Document OCR** - Scans receipts with camera/screen capture
- 📅 **Calendar Sync** - Tracks renewal dates from system calendars
- 🔔 **Notifications** - Desktop alerts for renewals

## Quick Start

```bash
# Install dependencies
npm install

# Run in development
npm run dev

# Build for your platform
npm run build
```

## Permissions Required

- **macOS**: Full Disk Access for Mail.app and Messages.app
- **Windows**: Outlook access, Your Phone app for SMS
- **Linux**: Access to Thunderbird, ADB for Android SMS

See [README.md](./README.md) for full documentation.

